<div class="feed-main">
<div class="content">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/29061672" target="_blank" data-id="3807643" data-za-element-name="Title">
GitHub 有什么用？放在上面的代码会泄漏吗？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/29061672/answer/43065180">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="12620022">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="43065180"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>364</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="count">364</span>
<span class="label sr-only">赞同</span>
</button>
<button class="down ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="label sr-only">反对</span>
</button>
</div>



<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">

<span class="summary-wrapper">
<span class="author-link-line">

<a class="author-link"
data-hovercard="p$t$trotyl"
target="_blank" href="/people/trotyl"
>Trotyl Yu</a></span><span title="某外包公司的搬砖工。" class="bio">
某外包公司的搬砖工。
</span>
</span>
</div>

<div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="364" data-async-voters="1">



<span class="voters text"><a href="#" class="more text"><span class="js-voteCount">364</span>&nbsp;人赞同</a></span>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text expandable js-collapse-body" data-resourceid="3807643" data-action="/answer/content" data-author-name="Trotyl Yu" data-entry-url="/question/29061672/answer/43065180">

<textarea hidden class="content">不仅会泄露，还会时不时有变态来监视（Watch）你，有食人族拿叉子叉（Fork）你，有小偷会标个星号（Star）等自己有空的时候来偷，有暴力狂会要求扯你（Pull Request），还会有处女座的来找你麻烦（Issue）。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;---&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;补充1:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;赞同评论中&lt;a href=&quot;//www.zhihu.com/people/ebd43a7511a9f063976b78cc355fe6b1&quot; data-hash=&quot;ebd43a7511a9f063976b78cc355fe6b1&quot; class=&quot;member_mention&quot; data-tip=&quot;p$b$ebd43a7511a9f063976b78cc355fe6b1&quot; data-hovercard=&quot;p$b$ebd43a7511a9f063976b78cc355fe6b1&quot;&gt;@方元溪&lt;/a&gt;的观点，Pull Request 严格地说应该是有受虐狂求着你去扯TA。。</textarea>


<div class="zh-summary summary clearfix">

不仅会泄露，还会时不时有变态来监视（Watch）你，有食人族拿叉子叉（Fork）你，有小偷会标个星号（Star）等自己有空的时候来偷，有暴力狂会要求扯你（Pull Request），还会有处女座的来找你麻烦（Issue）。 --- 补充1: 赞同评论中<a href="//www.zhihu.com/people/ebd43a7511a9f063976b78cc355fe6b1" data-hash="ebd43a7511a9f063976b78cc355fe6b1" class="member_mention" data-tip="p$b$ebd43a7511a9f063976b78cc355fe6b1" data-hovercard="p$b$ebd43a7511a9f063976b78cc355fe6b1">@方元溪</a>的观点，Pull Requ…

<a href="/question/29061672/answer/43065180" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>

</div>



<p class="visible-expanded"><a itemprop="url" class="answer-date-link meta-item" data-tooltip="s$t$发布于 2015-03-26" target="_blank" href="/question/29061672/answer/43065180">编辑于 2015-09-25</a></p>

</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-meta feed-meta">
