<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/38238351" target="_blank" data-id="7502587" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何看待微软 12 月 5 日宣布准备开源其 JavaScript 引擎 Chakra 的核心部分？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/38238351/answer/75496276">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="25622193">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="75496276"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>359</a>
