<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/31059577" target="_blank" data-id="4606436" data-za-element-name="Title">
做web前端开发，培训靠谱还是自学靠谱？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/31059577/answer/50936212">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="15775245">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="50936212"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>399</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
<button class="up ">
<i class="icon vote-arrow"></i>
<span class="count">399</span>
<span class="label sr-only">赞同</span>
