<div class="feed-main">
<div class="content">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/36069929" target="_blank" data-id="6634848" data-za-element-name="Title">
对于一般程序员来说，怎么防止为了潮流技术 疲于奔命？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/36069929/answer/65781878">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="21729493">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="65781878"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>355</a>
</div>

