<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/43165251" target="_blank" data-id="9474905" data-za-element-name="Title">
为什么全栈JavaScript经常被黑，而Java却不会被黑？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/43165251/answer/95373570">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="33591952">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="95373570"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>354</a>
</div>

<div class="zm-votebar">
