<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/36516604" target="_blank" data-id="6813810" data-za-element-name="Title">
react 有哪些最佳实践?
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/36516604/answer/82878351">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="28581414">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="82878351"> -->

