<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">

<span class="summary-wrapper">
<span class="author-link-line">

<a class="author-link"
data-hovercard="p$t$JimmyLv"
target="_blank" href="/people/JimmyLv"
>吕立青</a></span><span title="感性认识，理性认知" class="bio">
感性认识，理性认知
</span>
