<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/20936155" target="_blank" data-id="554990" data-za-element-name="Title">
WebStorm 有哪些过人之处？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/20936155/answer/16654794">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="1793852">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="16654794"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>353</a>
</div>

